flowchart LR
    User[Customer-service user] --> Host[AI Host / MCP Client]
    Host -->|Streamable HTTP + API key over TLS| Gateway[API Gateway / WAF]
    Gateway --> MCP[Retail MCP Server]

    subgraph Server[Retail MCP Server]
      Auth[Authentication Manager\nAPI key + RBAC]
      RM[Resource Manager\ncustomers / inventory / sales]
      TM[Tool Manager\norders / stock / tickets]
      Pool[Connection Pool]
      Cache[Cache Adapter]
      Metrics[Metrics + Audit]
      Auth --> RM
      Auth --> TM
      RM --> Cache
      RM --> Pool
      TM --> Pool
      RM --> Metrics
      TM --> Metrics
    end

    MCP --> Auth
    Pool --> DB[(PostgreSQL\nCRM / ERP projection)]
    Cache --> Redis[(Redis)]
    Metrics --> Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Metrics --> Logs[Central Audit Logs]
    Prometheus --> Grafana[Grafana + Alerts]
    DB -. adapters/events .-> CRM[CRM]
    DB -. adapters/events .-> ERP[ERP]
    DB -. adapters/events .-> Support[Support Platform]

